title: O'Neill Cranio collection with Jordy Smith (making of)
description: For Spring/Summer 2014, O'Neill has teamed up with much-loved Brazilian street artist Fabio Oliveira, better known as Cranio, for a limited edition signature series of graphic character-led tees, boardies and flip flops. The collaboration was inspired when the artist met O'Neill team rider Jordy Smith and drew some awe-inspiring graphics on his board during the 2013 Rio Pro.
